snippet.title: Cube Escape: Case 23 Walkthrough [Rusty Lake]
snippet.description:
Walkthrough for Cube Escape: Case 23

In Cube Escape: Case 23 you need to investigate the mysterious death of a woman. Collect all the evidence and discover the gateway to Rusty Lake.

Download now for iOS (Iphone and Ipad):
https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1020664488
Download on Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.RustyLake.CubeEscapeCase23
Or play on web:
http://www.rustylake.com/room-escape-games/cube-escape-case-23.html
